        <abstract> 
<p>Sends fourth volume of A. E. Brehm’s <hi rend="italic">Thierleben</hi>. First three sent at V. O. Kovalevsky’s request. Asks CD’s support for an English edition, since this is the first extensive popular work based on CD’s theory.</p> 
